title: True Trans - Against Me! [2013] - Lossy
description:
Contains the two songs "FuckMyLife666" and "True 

Trans Soul Rebel" in MP3 320 quality
------------------------------------------------

Excerpt from the wiki entry on the Single
------------------------------------------------

"True Trans" is a single from Against Me!, 

released as a digital single on July 12, 2013, 

on Total Treble Music.

The single features two acoustic versions of 

songs that are expected to appear on Against 

Me!'s sixth studio album, Transgender Dysphoria 

Blues, which is likely to release towards the 

end of 2013. The song "True Trans Soul Rebel" 

has been played at live shows since May 30, 

2012.

The artwork for the single features Jame 

"Buffalo Bill" Gumb from 1991 movie The Silence 

of the Lambs, who is a male serial killer often 

wrongly described as transgendered.


Official website: http://www.againstme.net/
